casebody.data:
NATIONAL ASSOCIATION FOR THE ADVANCEMENT OF MULTIJURISDICTION PRACTICE, et al., petitioners,
v.
Beryl A. HOWELL, Chief Judge, United States District Court for the District of Columbia, et al. No. 17-409. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 30, 2017.

Motion of Jennifer Low for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.
